The spokesman for the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">German</ENAMEX> government <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Fughr</ENAMEX> expressed on <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">the 31st</ENAMEX> that , <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Germany</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Russia</ENAMEX> are prepared to strengthen international anti-smuggling activities of nuclear material , and also proposed to strengthen communication of information in this area by intelligence departments from both countries .
